text:
Umm... Excuse me...
Are you an idol?

I saw you before, you know.
You were wearing really cool clothes.

You right, Fuyu is an Idol.
We're called "Straylight."

Thank you for watching.
We'll do it again tomorrow, so please come watch again!

Fufu, thank you.
Well then, until next time.

Kids are pretty sharp, huh.
I've got to be careful.

Haha, but as expected of Fuyuko. 
You weren't caught off guard and your fanservice was flawless.

Obviously.
Even children are our precious fans.
